                  </persName>
            . I bought an odd left boot of the prisoner - I do not know whether this is it: but Mr. Fair had it three days in his possession - about a month ago I bought it for 1s., and sent it by my husband to have a fellow made.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18340904-138-person811">
                  JOHN 
                  TOBY
               <interp inst="t18340904-138-person811" type="surname" value="TOBY"></interp>
